'''亞瑟·迪宏·理特'''（{{lang-en|'''Arthur Dehon Little'''}}，{{bd|1863年|12月15日|1935年|8月1日}}），[[美國|美國]][[化學家|化學家]]及[[化學工程師|化學工程師]]。他創立了{{le|理特顧問公司|Arthur D. Little}}，並對[[麻省理工學院|麻省理工學院]]建立[[化學工程|化學工程]]學門做出重大貢獻。他在1916年提出了[[單元操作|單元操作]]這個術語及概念來解釋化工製程<ref>{{cite web |title=Arther Dehon Little |work=Scatter Acorns That Oaks May Grow |url=http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/adlittle/mit-connection.html |publisher=MIT Libraries |accessdate=13 November 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090311123042/http://libraries.mit.edu/archives/exhibits/adlittle/mit-connection.html |archive-date=2009-03-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Servos">{{cite journal|last1=Servos|first1=John W.|title=The Industrial Relations of Science: Chemical Engineering at MIT, 1900-1939|journal=Isis|date=December 1980|volume=71|issue=4|pages=530–549|doi=10.1086/352591|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/230499?seq=1#page_scan_tab_contents|accessdate=30 November 2016|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513083801/https://www.jstor.org/stable/230499?seq=1#page_scan_tab_contents|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並促進工業界[[研究開發|研究開發]]的概念。<ref name="Book">{{cite book|last1=Servos|first1=John W.|title=Physical chemistry from Ostwald to Pauling : the making of a science in America|date=1990|publisher=Princeton University Press|location=Princeton, N.J.|isbn=0-691-08566-8|page=208, 363|edition=2nd|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1UZjU2WfLAoC&pg=PA208|access-date=2016-12-29|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513145049/https://books.google.com/books?id=1UZjU2WfLAoC&pg=PA208|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CHF">{{cite web|title=Arthur D. Little, William H. Walker, and Warren K. Lewis|url=https://www.chemheritage.org/historical-profile/arthur-d-little-william-h-walker-and-warren-k-lewis|website=Chemical Heritage Foundation|accessdate=30 November 2016|archive-date=2017-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929092937/https://www.chemheritage.org/historical-profile/arthur-d-little-william-h-walker-and-warren-k-lewis|dead-url=no}}</ref>

